This is a collection of more or less practical examples of CFEngine 3 language.

Aleksey Tsalolikhin used it to learn and then to teach CFEngine 3.

It is intended to supplement the documentation from cfengine.com

Professional CFEngine 3 training is available from www.verticalsysadmin.com

How to use this collection:

The examples are arranged alphanumerically by filename in logical order. 
Please list them with "ls -1" to get the alphanumeric sorting.  Go through
in order.

Additional CFEngine resources are available at www.verticalsysadmin.com/cfengine/

Enjoy learning CFEngine 3!

Best,
